{"tid":844393,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"全球首架波音777客機退役　美國航空博物館公開展覽","createTime":"2018-10-02T00:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T13:57:38.000Z","uid":81228,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a1798fbd8d631b9311b1d851be846468e05b3e14","tid":844393,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923585/org/62efb2facb7df6bbed40a84794e20745.jpg/h1Ihl-RgczLisoJlBHEUmQJJjoefaqIv68p7X-vKe18?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923585%2Forg%2F62efb2facb7df6bbed40a84794e20745.jpg%2Fh1Ihl-RgczLisoJlBHEUmQJJjoefaqIv68p7X-vKe18%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e91a0ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923546/org/fefc21d70f00ec10e294a47a0143990e.jpg/FJyupbJzQ2pAjOJBEj0Ua-cqUowiow56_dNx8_3TcfM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923546%2Forg%2Ffefc21d70f00ec10e294a47a0143990e.jpg%2FFJyupbJzQ2pAjOJBEj0Ua-cqUowiow56_dNx8_3TcfM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ee0ab1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：首架波音777-200客機B-HNL於1994年落成，並於2000年加入成為國泰航空機隊一份子。（皮馬航空航天博物館 Facebook圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923554/org/7a35836e0810c5ee0d0c14090c9f527f.jpg/qr4OzDFaeVsSOjKbU84xiupkHnYbEv3fQNjyOkDY8jo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923554%2Forg%2F7a35836e0810c5ee0d0c14090c9f527f.jpg%2Fqr4OzDFaeVsSOjKbU84xiupkHnYbEv3fQNjyOkDY8jo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=168a5c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：B-HNL經過18年歲月，合共為國泰擔任25,519次航班，累積飛行時間為49,687小時。（國泰航空公司Facebook圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923550/org/278035c11c8acd41ef13e48d2813a001.jpg/0m_nPbUGOxdK1gEJ3RzMku6P8-BSO_yZ9zb3Bvc29wY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923550%2Forg%2F278035c11c8acd41ef13e48d2813a001.jpg%2F0m_nPbUGOxdK1gEJ3RzMku6P8-BSO_yZ9zb3Bvc29wY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6223c74e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：B-HNL於2018年5月退出商業飛行名單，國泰並與製造商波音違成協議，決定捐出B-HNL作展覽用途。（國泰航空公司Facebook圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923545/org/2ad8d69966a5c7f4eedfd3d4caf3f92a.jpg/X7FQfpzGDvDZkGK2tGxJd1yXP550pweOGVaImRlWiJk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923545%2Forg%2F2ad8d69966a5c7f4eedfd3d4caf3f92a.jpg%2FX7FQfpzGDvDZkGK2tGxJd1yXP550pweOGVaImRlWiJk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6ff5aa62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：777-200型客機是全球首架雙引擎飛機，以及是最先使用全數碼電傳操縱（fly-by-wire control）的機種。（皮馬航空航天博物館 Facebook圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923548/org/c986a5e759c819171093d782b10f5e2c.jpg/HqGu30ed2xMjav-BKss8J-OeqD8dDVPpe_A02nvwNNo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923548%2Forg%2Fc986a5e759c819171093d782b10f5e2c.jpg%2FHqGu30ed2xMjav-BKss8J-OeqD8dDVPpe_A02nvwNNo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8e80119e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：B-HNL於9月19日飛抵皮馬航空航天博物館，機師在艙內拍下照片留為紀念。將圖片放大，可見機艙內只剩下中間的座位，感覺特別寬敞。（國泰航空公司Facebook圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923547/org/898913695cc1b6fcb59952d5491796ff.jpg/1YDT01KyfNWSfV8helXMmNs95S_OlseRVyNuKFcjbig?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923547%2Forg%2F898913695cc1b6fcb59952d5491796ff.jpg%2F1YDT01KyfNWSfV8helXMmNs95S_OlseRVyNuKFcjbig%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4937901a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：國泰航空與英航、全日空、澳航、日航、美國航空等國際航空公司在波音設計777型客機時提供意見，因此今次B-HNL退役時，波音特意向國泰致敬。（皮馬航空航天博物館 Facebook圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923553/org/c556464a53fc7acb5fb04fb84733e010.jpg/feflD8DSOUmf6APo24v9UGiVQclTj-xBFK8PDRSvDw0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923553%2Forg%2Fc556464a53fc7acb5fb04fb84733e010.jpg%2FfeflD8DSOUmf6APo24v9UGiVQclTj-xBFK8PDRSvDw0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d5d844cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：國泰航空行政總裁何杲（Rupert Hogg）表示，公司旗下的777-200型客機在近20年一直運作良好，並準備開始引進新機種取代，預計在2021年正式引入波音777-9型客機。（皮馬航空航天博物館 Facebook圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923549/org/823efd4d1e01ceacccc06484cd7b8993.jpg/nZcqgWM7SxL1TwCCJP84WNfJoYH7hTh4dtfSz3bX0s8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923549%2Forg%2F823efd4d1e01ceacccc06484cd7b8993.jpg%2FnZcqgWM7SxL1TwCCJP84WNfJoYH7hTh4dtfSz3bX0s8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=20e70d4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：B-HNL在美國亞利桑那州圖森（Tucson）的戴維斯&mdash;蒙森空軍基地（Davis-Monthan Air Force Base），其後被拖到附近的皮馬航空航天博物館，準備展開第二人生。（皮馬航空航天博物館 Facebook圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923552/org/ba19be33aff2b4158b3c3b9b1df20636.jpg/LCI77RFnPLVl8n8-WlPVPa7ykjHHapSsj5aSvY-Wkr0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923552%2Forg%2Fba19be33aff2b4158b3c3b9b1df20636.jpg%2FLCI77RFnPLVl8n8-WlPVPa7ykjHHapSsj5aSvY-Wkr0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4bc5c937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：B-HNL飛抵皮馬航空航天博物館後，將成為館內300架展品之一，除了它之外，館內亦收藏了世上首架有人駕駛的動力飛行器萊特飛行器（Wright Flyer）、波音787型夢幻客機（Dreamliner）及不同類型的戰機等。（皮馬航空航天博物館 Facebook圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1923551/org/d0b2e19de92ec1d7436c38cb1a4c8ae2.jpg/ar-QjuS4KvwuE-UBzVhNvDLjyJu67fz8kPQxnZD0MZ0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1923551%2Forg%2Fd0b2e19de92ec1d7436c38cb1a4c8ae2.jpg%2Far-QjuS4KvwuE-UBzVhNvDLjyJu67fz8kPQxnZD0MZ0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7585420d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n777-200客機退役：雖然B-HNL已經退役，國泰另一架777型客機卻成為國際新聞焦點：該架飛機在大修後飛回香港時被發現公司名稱少了一個「F」，結果國泰需要「退貨」，但同時亦不失幽默感，自嘲這架飛機是「期間限定」。（國泰航空公司Facebook圖片）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/241830/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E6%9E%B6%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3777%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F%E9%80%80%E5%BD%B9-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%B1%95%E8%A6%BD#media_id=1923551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F241830%2F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%259E%25B6%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E9%259F%25B3777%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%25BD%25B9-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%25A6%25BD%23media_id%3D1923551&d=lejSInp4vmoBWxV5B205Smi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=742b9cc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/241830/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E6%9E%B6%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3777%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F%E9%80%80%E5%BD%B9-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%B1%95%E8%A6%BD#media_id=1923551</a>"},{"pid":"fa40a21262f6a21de02195e89e0037891980d521","tid":844393,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"好撚想去美國啲戰機戰艦同飛機博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4392c9f744633c139003dcb0b489ec9ed688c462","tid":844393,"uid":213413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:42:36.000Z","msg":"ITVV 有集 Cockpit 講呢隻機拎ETOPS Certification <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a792d3b6fc89d82c0ed6f31ebc1fb5d898c197","tid":844393,"uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:44:13.000Z","msg":"十幾年就退役渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nB52五十年都未退役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fad928790249e49d1dbd58e55fed21f81ec8342","tid":844393,"uid":57,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"62a792d3b6fc8